OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780643100
OL,3,CTwo charged in relation to Southampton
OL,4,Cdisorder sparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FTwo men have been charged following
OL,7,Fdisorder in Southampton on Tuesday
OL,8,Fevening sparked by the murder of Henry
OL,9,FNowak.
OL,11,FMatt Styler, 50, has been charged with
OL,12,Fassaulting a police officer (assault
OL,13,Fof an emergency worker), and Daniel
OL,14,FFrost, 44, has been charged with
OL,15,Fviolent disorder and possession of an
OL,16,Foffensive weapon.
OL,18,FThey will appear at Southampton
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court today (4 June)
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
