OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1780643100
OL,3,CTwo charged in relation to Southampton
OL,4,Cdisorder sparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,FSophie Stevens, Deputy Chief Crown
OL,7,FProsecutor for CPS Wessex, said: "We
OL,8,Fhave decided to prosecute Matt Styler
OL,9,Fwith assault of an emergency worker.
OL,11,F"Later our out of hours team CPS
OL,12,FDirect also directed that Daniel Frost
OL,13,Fwas charged with violent disorder and
OL,14,Fpossession of an offensive weapon `
OL,15,Fthis followed an investigation into
OL,16,Falleged offending following protests
OL,17,Fheld in Southampton on Tuesday evening.
