OL,3,CTwo charged in relation to Southampton
OL,4,Cdisorder sparked by Henry Nowak murder
OL,6,F"Our prosecutors have worked to
OL,7,Festablish that there is sufficient
OL,8,Fevidence to bring the case to court
OL,9,Fand that it is in the public interest
OL,10,Fto pursue criminal proceedings.
OL,12,F"We have worked closely with Hampshire
OL,13,Fpolice as it has carried out its
OL,14,Finvestigation."
OL,16,FThis is breaking news. More follows.
